 this is one you could bear-ly dare to miss.\nBest of luck human, we think you'll need it...", "short_description": "What do you do when the local teddy bear factory gets taken over by an evil bear turning all the cute cuddly teddy bears against you? Play Sneaky Bears to find out. This new VR action adventure game is all you need to get involved in one of the most exciting adventures of all time. Finish the game to play against your friends in the leaderboard measured \u201cSurvival mode\u201d. This game just keeps giving...\n#dontletthemcatchya"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.iubenda.com/privacy-policy/377885", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "http://globalagents.warducks.com/about/terms.html", "publisher_name": "WarDucks LTD", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://www.sneakybearsvr.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": null, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": null, "genres": ["ACTION", "NARRATIVE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": null, "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["TOUCHPAD"], "supported_player_modes": [], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "328749599178416"}, "review_messages": ["", "Please remove the cardboard VR box from the end of your video. Also remove all the text overlays from your screenshots, we do not allow these in screenshots."]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/11162737_1948439828761445_3792758135878320128_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=KAc5XQAgx3UQ7kNvgHZstcB&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYA0tFf9-WCg6VqMyVV9empZSgKO_UiZgCXBTMSbX93QCg&oe=6742FF03"}, "is_concept": false, "is_te